T01TD1161E:230a-1: shuddha aa bhi she ka n'a ma sto tra:/
T01TD1161E:230a-3: sangs rgyas dbang bskur ba zhes bya ba'i bstod pa /
T01TD1161E:230a-4: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1161E:230a-5: de nas bskal pa grangs med gsum //
T01TD1161E:230a-6: pha rol phyin rnams rdzogs pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230a-7: thub pa lha rnams kyi ston pa //
T01TD1161E:230a-8: mtho ris nas ni mi nang gshegs //
T01TD1161E:230a-9: nyi ma'i rigs te zla ba yi //
T01TD1161E:230a-10: sa yi bdag po zas gtsang dang //
T01TD1161E:230a-11: gtso mo sgyu 'phrul lha mo yi //
T01TD1161E:230a-12: mngal du nyid mtshams sbyor bar mdzad //
T01TD1161E:230a-13: der ni rin chen khang gnas shing //
T01TD1161E:230a-14: lha yi mchog rnams bstod byed la ;
T01TD1161E:230a-15: / de la gsung ni mthon po yis //
T01TD1161E:230a-16: dam pa'i chos ni ston par mdzad //
T01TD1161E:230a-17: lha rnams thal mo sbyar byas te //
T01TD1161E:230a-18: dus gsum du ni der blta ba //
T01TD1161E:230a-19: rdul med mu tig phreng ba ni //
T01TD1161E:230a-21: bdud rtsi rab sbyin gzugs can te //
T01TD1161E:230a-22: de 'os lha mo mdzes par gyur//
T01TD1161E:230a-23: zla ba shin tu gsal ba'am //
T01TD1161E:230a-26: yid la re ba'i don rdzogs mdzad //
T01TD1161E:230a-27: de ni 'dod la stsol ba ste //
T01TD1161E:230a-28: 'dod pa thams cad phun tshogs mdzad //
T01TD1161E:230a-29: skyed mos tshal ni lumbi n'ir //
T01TD1161E:230a-30: 'jig rten gtso mo sor gyur te ;
T01TD1161E:230a-31: / sa bdag dang ni slas rnams dang //
T01TD1161E:230a-32: mdun na 'don dang lhan cig gnas //
T01TD1161E:230a-33: der ni mya ngan med pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230a-34: yal ga la 'jus brtul zhugs gnas //
T01TD1161E:230a-35: mkha' la lha yi bu mo rnams //
T01TD1161E:230a-36: zla ba dang ni skar tshogs 'dra //
T01TD1161E:230a-37: skar ma rgyal la bab pa na //
T01TD1161E:230a-38: de'i sras rtsib ma'i logs nas ni ;
T01TD1161E:230a-39: /'gro la phan pa mkhyen pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230a-40: nyi ma shar ba bzhin du byung //
T01TD1161E:230a-41: mtshan mchog yang dag rdzogs pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230a-42: gtso bo nyid kyi sku yi 'od //
T01TD1161E:230a-44: phyogs rnams rab tu snang bar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230a-45: brgya byin ma ma'i cha byad can //
T01TD1161E:230a-46: smin ma bskyod pas zlog pa mdzad //
T01TD1161E:230a-47: sa la gom bdun bor ba na //
T01TD1161E:230a-48: gter dang pad+mas brgyan par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230a-49: bdag gi skye ba tha ma ni //
T01TD1161E:230a-50: 'di yin yang srid yod min zhes //
T01TD1161E:230a-51: snyan pa'i gsung ni bsgrags nas kyang //
T01TD1161E:230a-52: phyogs rnams kun du gzigs par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230a-53: nyi zla rin chen bum pa las //
T01TD1161E:230b-0: @230b dro grang chu yi rgyun gnyis ni //
T01TD1161E:230b-1: dri ma med pa'i nam mkha' las //
T01TD1161E:230b-2: de yi dbu la bab bar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-3: bde gshegs 'gro ba'i bla ma ni //
T01TD1161E:230b-4: rin chen sna tshogs bkram pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230b-5: seng ge'i gdan ni mthon po la //
T01TD1161E:230b-6: dgyes pas der ni bzhugs par 'gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-7: brgya byin gnas kyi chu bo dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-8: 'jug ngogs las blangs lha yi chu //
T01TD1161E:230b-9: gser las byas pa'i bum pa yis //
T01TD1161E:230b-10: lha rnams kyis ni dbang bskur bstabs //
T01TD1161E:230b-11: lha yi gos dang phreng ba dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-12: bstod pa la ni brtson pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230b-13: tshogs rnams du ma 'dus pa yis //
T01TD1161E:230b-14: lha yi tshal ni gang bar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-15: rnga sgra rnams dang ca co yis //
T01TD1161E:230b-16: mkha' dbyings ma lus khyab par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-17: nam mkha' las ni me tog char //
T01TD1161E:230b-18: rgyun mi 'chad par bab par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-19: mand'ar me tog gcal bkram pas //
T01TD1161E:230b-20: gnas gtsang ma yi gnas ltar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-21: ga bur tsandan phye ma yis //
T01TD1161E:230b-22: 'jig rten mgon la gtor bar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-23: ri bo rgya mtshor bcas pa dag / gar mkhan gyi ni gos ltar g-yo //
T01TD1161E:230b-24: bcud rnams sna tshogs 'dzin pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230b-25: sa dag rnam drug g-yos par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-26: gung ba rnams ni sgra sgrogs shing //
T01TD1161E:230b-27: dus rnams kun du byung ba yi //
T01TD1161E:230b-28: shing rnams rang nyid 'dud pa dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-29: me tog rnams ni 'bor bar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-30: blon po rgan dang mdun na 'don //
T01TD1161E:230b-31: bkra shis dag ni 'don par byed //
T01TD1161E:230b-32: sa dang mkha' dang grub pa dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-33: mi 'am ci dang lhan cig spyod //
T01TD1161E:230b-34: nags na gnas pa'i lha rnams dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-35: lha dang grub pa rig 'dzin mi //
T01TD1161E:230b-36: nang gi slas kyi bud med kyang //
T01TD1161E:230b-37: rab tu dga' bas gar yang byed //
T01TD1161E:230b-38: long bas mig dang 'on pas thos //
T01TD1161E:230b-39: lkugs pa rnams ni sgra gsal dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-40: nad pa nad las thar ba dag / skad cig der ni thob par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-41: ri dags bya dang sdig sprul dag / phan tshun 'tshe bar 'dod pa yi //
T01TD1161E:230b-42: sems can thams cad de yi tshe //
T01TD1161E:230b-43: rtsod med 'tshe ba med par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-44: de tshe gang yang sdug bsngal dang //
T01TD1161E:230b-45: nyes spyod byung bar ma gyur to //
T01TD1161E:230b-47: bde zhing lo yar legs par gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-48: de tshe kun du'ang mdun du ni //
T01TD1161E:230b-49: gter rnams der ni byung bar gyur //
T01TD1161E:230b-50: de tshe srid gsum rgyas par ni //
T01TD1161E:231a-2: rgyal ba dbang bskur bsod nams gang //
T01TD1161E:231a-3: bsod nams ldan pa'i sems kyis ni //
T01TD1161E:231a-4: nyan par byed pa de dag la //
T01TD1161E:231a-5: phun sum tshogs kun lag mthil gnas //
T01TD1161E:231a-6: tshe dang nad med dbang phyug dang //
T01TD1161E:231a-7: dgra zhi rgyas dang rgyal dang grags //
T01TD1161E:231a-8: rdzogs sangs yon tan sgrogs pa yi //
T01TD1161E:231a-9: dad pa'i mi yis thob par 'gyur //
T01TD1161E:231a-10: sangs rgyas dbang bskur ba zhes bya ba'i bstod pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1161E:231a-12: // / lo ts'a ba chen po rin chen bzang pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa//
